"&#xa0;\nWritten evidence from the Nursing and Midwifery Council (NMC 0001)&#xa0;Introduction&#xa0;\nResponding to Francis&#xa0;\n5.1\n&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; \nTo evaluate our education standards and review our code to ensure that Francis themes such as candour and compassion are appropriately covered.\n5.2\n&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; \nTo raise our profile as recommended by the Francis report so that patients, the public and employers understand our role and get the support they need if they have concerns about a nurse or midwife.\n5.3\n&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; \nTo implement the changes to our fitness to practise legislation announced by the Prime Minister in response to the Francis report and thereby deliver improvements to the timeliness and quality of our casework.\n5.4\n&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; \nTo strengthen our collaborative work with other regulators – we have revised our memorandum of understanding with the CQC and will have new protocols for information sharing and joint work by the end of 2013. We want to extend this work to other UK regulators in 2014.\nCode\n&#xa0;\nEducation\n&#xa0;Fitness to practise&#xa0;\nRevalidation&#xa0;Overseas registration &#xa0;\nRevision of the EU recognition of professional qualifications directive&#xa0;\nTesting of the English language competence of EU migrants&#xa0;\nRegistration fee&#xa0;\nRaising our profile&#xa0;\nOrganisational health of the NMC&#xa0;\nLeadership and governance\n&#xa0;\nFinance and ICT\n&#xa0;\n36.1\n&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; \nBetter links between the register and case management systems mitigating the risk that case outcomes are not reflected on the register\n36.2\n&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; \nUpgrades to outdated desktop technology \n36.3\n&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; \nInitial online registration facilities and technical roadmap for revalidation\n36.4\n&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; \nNew\n \nsystem for customer relationship management \n36.5\n&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; \nEnhanced reports and dashboards for fitness to practise.\nStaff culture and turnover\n&#xa0;\nConcluding comments&#xa0;September 2013\n              \n              \n"